attacks.name: Thunderbolt

ability.name: Last Pattern

ability.name: Surrender Now

name: Bill's Analysis

name: Последняя Битва Блэйна
text: You can play this card only when it is the last card in your hand.\n\nDraw 2 cards for each Fire Pokémon you have in play.

name: Brock's Grit
text: Shuffle 6 in any combination of Pokémon and basic Energy cards from your discard pile into your deck.

name: Brock's Pewter City Gym
text: Onix-GX (both yours and your opponent's) take 40 less damage from the opponent's attacks (after applying Weakness and Resistance).

name: Brock's Training

name: Erika's Hospitality

name: Giovanni's Exile

name: Jessie & James

name: Koga's Trap

name: Misty's Cerulean City Gym

name: Misty's Determination

name: Misty's Water Command
